&lt;h3 id=&#34;cp-legend-c-consumer-p-producer-both&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#cp-legend-c-consumer-p-producer-both&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; C/P legend: C = Consumer, P = Producer, * = both&lt;/h3&gt;

